name: Pre
description: PopulateChunkEvent.Pre is fired just before a chunk is populated a terrain feature. This event is fired just before terrain feature generation in ChunkProviderEnd.populate(int, int) , ChunkProviderOverworld.populate(int, int) , and ChunkProviderHell.populate(int, int) . This event is not Cancelable . This event does not have a result. HasResult This event is fired on the MinecraftForge.EVENT_BUS .
